value: LEVEL 35 201 ELIZABETH STREET, SYDNEY, 2000, NSW, Australia

5621 - Women's Clothing Stores Summary > BOTTEGA VENETA AUSTRALIA PTY LTD is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover women's clothing stores. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. BOTTEGA VENETA AUSTRALIA PTY LTD is headquartered in Sydney, New South Wales. It is headed by director Albin Cheng. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $33.01 million. Its net profit totalled $422,000. BOTTEGA VENETA AUSTRALIA PTY LTD forms part of the retail trade industry sector.
